AREAREN.CBS   Renumbers areas in H:\MAX\filearea.ctl, starting from the current line.
BAMBI.ANS     An example of a VT100 animated image.
CONNECT.MNU   Menu for the TRANSIVE program.
DEL-.CBS      Removes line breaks from text.
DELESC.CBS    Removes ESCAPE sequences from text.
F2F.CBS       Reformats a file generated by the command `dir > file` into the `files.bbs` format.
FILES_EN.BBS  A list of files in this directory, including comments (English, sorted).
FILES_RU.BBS  A list of files in this directory, including comments (Russian, semi-sorted).
ID.CBS        Login script for id.ecos.kharkov.ua.
KERMIT.DMP    Terminal session dump (Kermit).
KPI.CBS       Login script for kpi.kharkov.ua.
KURSIV.CBS    Processes text "highlighting" (spacing/emphasis).
lamps.CBS     Paginates text.
MON.CBS       Monitor utility featuring my custom controller.
PAGER.CBS     Paginates text (splits it into pages).
SET-.CBS      Formats dialogue sections within text.
SETPAR.CBS    Formats paragraphs.
TCAPTST.CBB   Outputs a dump generated by TERMDUMP.CBS to the terminal. Used for debugging termcap files and viewing ANSI images.
TCAPTST.CBS   Displays a terminal dump (generated by TERMDUMP.CBS) on the screen. Used for debugging termcap files and viewing ANSI art.
TERM.CBS      ANSI terminal emulator that logs received characters.
TERMDUMP.CBS  Logs characters received by the terminal to the file `termlog.log`.
TRANSIVE.CBS  Program for exchanging data with another controller.
TXTCNV.ASM    Subroutine for the TRANSIVE program (source code).
TXTCNV.BIN    Subroutine for the TRANSIVE program (binary).
UNINDENT.CBS  Removes text indentation (shifts text to the left margin).
UNPAGER.CBS   Removes pagination (page breaks).
VI.DMP        Terminal session dump (vi).
VT100.DMP     Terminal session dump (VT100).
VT200.DMP     Terminal session dump (VT200).
XMAS.ANS      An example of an ANSI image for testing terminal ANSI emulation.
